title: US Rowing Members, Selected Biased Cities, USA 2009
name: US Rowing Members, Selected Biased Cities, USA 2009
description: This is a geocoded list of US Rowing members for selected US cities. The list is comprised of those cities that Fortius One employees/rowers came up with when asked which cities in the US are the most known rowing cities. This is a biased list and is in no way intended to be the end all be all of best rowing cities in the US. The purpose is to see whether or not the perception of a city as a best rowing city can actually be backed up with raw data to determine if it truly is a best rowing city in the US.
